### Test Register - Username already exists (should fail)
POST https://localhost:5010/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenDangNhap": "testuser",
  "matKhau": "123456",
  "vaiTro_Id": 2
}

### Test Register - Short username (should fail)
POST https://localhost:5010/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenDangNhap": "ab",
  "matKhau": "123456",
  "vaiTro_Id": 2
}

### Test Register - Short password (should fail)
POST https://localhost:5010/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenDangNhap": "testuser3",
  "matKhau": "12345",
  "vaiTro_Id": 2
